title: Dash regex filter example
content:
import dash
import dash_core_components as dcc
import dash_html_components as html
from dash.dependencies import Input, Output
import plotly.express as px
import re

# Créer un dataframe avec des données aléatoires
df = px.data.gapminder().query("year == 2007")

# Créer une application dash
app = dash.Dash(__name__)

# Définir le layout de l'application
app.layout = html.Div([
    # Un titre
    html.H1("Filtrer les légendes avec une expression regex"),
    # Un graphique plotly
    dcc.Graph(id="graph"),
    # Une text box pour entrer le regex
    html.Div([
        html.Label("Entrez une expression regex:"),
        dcc.Input(id="regex-input", type="text", value=".*")
    ])
])

# Définir une fonction qui met à jour le graphique en fonction du regex
@app.callback(
    Output("graph", "figure"),
    Input("regex-input", "value")
)
def update_graph(regex):
    # Créer un masque booléen pour filtrer les lignes du dataframe qui correspondent au regex
    mask = df["country"].apply(lambda x: bool(re.match(regex, x)))
    # Créer un sous-dataframe avec les lignes filtrées
    filtered_df = df[mask]
    # Créer un graphique plotly avec le sous-dataframe
    fig = px.scatter(filtered_df, x="gdpPercap", y="lifeExp", size="pop", color="continent", hover_name="country", log_x=True, size_max=60)
    # Retourner le graphique
    return fig

# Lancer l'application
app.run(debug=True, renderer='browser')

deck = {

"7s", "7c", "7d", "7h",
"6s", "6c", "6d", "6h",
"5s", "5c", "5d", "5h",
"4s", "4c", "4d", "4h",
"3s", "3c", "3d", "3h",
"2s", "2c", "2d", "2h"
}

math.randomseed(os.time())

function shuffle(deck)
    for i = #deck, 2, -1 do
		local j = math.random(i)
		deck[i], deck[j] = deck[j], deck[i]
	end
end



shuffle(deck)

textutils.tabulate(deck)

The dystopian version of superintelligence is illustrated with frequency by leaders in the technology industry, and is famously depicted by Hollywood in films like Terminator, 
or more recently Ex Machina, and even the Avengers. The “furious deity A.I.” is a story you know, because it is the story you are constantly told: we build the thinking machine, 
it surpasses our abilities in every way, and it destroys us for one of any number of reasons.Maybe it perceives us as a threat. Maybe we’re just in its way, 
and it hardly perceives us at all — mankind, a disposable insect race.

There are of course many arguments in opposition to the now ubiquitous concept of our apocalypse by artificial intelligence. 
I myself have called into question the logic of such dystopian arguments in Anatomy of Next. But our subject here is less pertaining to the nature of the conscious machine than 
it is to the way we talk about this subject, and what it means. First, consider that most of the artificial intelligence depicted in culture looks human, a representation with 
no basis in technological reality. Then, the true scope of the Singularity is almost impossible to predict, which begs a question: where are these opinions about the broadly 
unknowable coming from?

select soc.user_id,
       c.payment_type,
       c.flag_card,
       soi.price,
       soi.payment_date,
       soi.send_date,
       sop.payment_type,
       sop.value,
       sop.discount,
       sop.quantity,
       soc.consumed,
       i.cart_item_id,
       i.price,
       i.send_date,
       i.installment,
       ci.last_invoice_status,
       ci.discount_price,
       c.status,
       sop.created_at,
       soi.created_at
from store_oneclick_invoice soi
         join store_oneclick_purchase sop on soi.store_oneclick_purchase_id = sop.id
         join store_oneclick_campaign soc on sop.oneclick_campaign_id = soc.id
         join invoice i on soi.invoice_id = i.id
         join cart_items ci on i.cart_item_id = ci.id
         join cart c on ci.id_cart = c.id
         join user u on c.user_id = u.id
where sop.quantity > 1
# and YEAR(sop.created_at) = YEAR(now())
# and month(sop.created_at) = MONTH(now())
order by sop.created_at desc;

class VirtualMachine:
    def __init__(self):
        self.registers = [0] * 4  # 4 регистра общего назначения
        self.memory = [0] * 256  # Виртуальная память размером 256 байт

    def load_program(self, program):
        address = 0
        for instruction in program:
            self.memory[address] = instruction
            address += 1

    def execute(self):
        pc = 0  # Счетчик команд
        while True:
            print(self.registers)
            opcode = self.memory[pc]
            if opcode == 0:  # Остановка программы
                break
            elif opcode == 1:  # Load
                reg_index = self.memory[pc + 1]
                address = self.memory[pc + 2]
                self.registers[reg_index] = self.memory[address]
                pc += 3
            elif opcode == 2:  # Write
                reg_index = self.memory[pc + 1]
                address = self.memory[pc + 2]
                self.memory[address] = self.registers[reg_index]
                pc += 3
            elif opcode == 3:  # Addition
                reg_index = self.memory[pc + 1]
                reg_index1 = self.memory[pc + 2]
                reg_index2 = self.memory[pc + 3]
                self.registers[reg_index] = self.registers[reg_index1] + self.registers[reg_index2]
                pc += 4
            else:
                print(f"Unknown opcode: {opcode}")
                break

# Пример программы в виде десятичного кода
program = [
    1, 0, 10,   # Загрузить значение из адреса 10 в регистр 0
    1, 1, 20,   # Загрузить значение из адреса 20 в регистр 1
    3, 2, 0, 1,  # Сложить значения из регистров 0 и 1 и сохранить результат в регистр 2
    2, 2, 30,   # Сохранить значение из регистра 2 в адрес 30
    0          # Остановка программы
]


vm = VirtualMachine()
vm.load_program(program)

# Выполняем
vm.execute()

# Выводим результат из памяти
print(vm.memory[30])

Modem = peripheral.find('modem',rednet.open)

--Replace with actual account db
AccountDetails = {
    admin = "admin"
}
IncomingRequests = {}
rednet.host("AmaZincServer", "Main")

while true do
    local eventData = {os.pullEvent()}
    local event = eventData[1]
    if event == "rednet_message" then
        local id, message
        event, id, message = unpack(eventData)
        if(message.type == "login") then
            local username = message.username
            local password = message.password
            local pasGet = AccountDetails[username]
            if pasGet == nil then
                rednet.send(id, {type="loginError", message="Incorrect Username!"}, "login")
            elseif password ~= pasGet then
                rednet.send(id, {type="loginError", message="Incorrect Password!"}, "login")
            else
                rednet.send(id, {type="loginSuccess", message="Neat!"}, "login")
            end
        end
            
       end
    end

title: Untitled
content:
print("[INFO] Importing modules...")
import os
import discord
from discord.ext import commands
import platform
import aiosqlite
from dotenv import load_dotenv
print("[INFO] Modules imported!")
print(f"[DEBUG] OS: {platform.system()}")
load_dotenv()
token = os.getenv("TOKEN")

async def get_prefix(client: discord.Client, message: discord.Message):
    if not message.guild:
        return "."
    await client.db.execute("SELECT prefix, mention FROM guilds WHERE id = $1", (str(message.guild.id),))
    res = await client.cur.fetchone()
    if not res:
        return commands.when_mentioned_or(".")(client, message)
    if res[1] == 1:
        return commands.when_mentioned_or(res[0])(client, message)
    else:
        return res[0]

class MyClient(commands.AutoShardedBot):
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__(command_prefix=get_prefix, intents=discord.Intents.all(), case_insensitive=False, activity=discord.Game(name="with your heart"), status=discord.Status.online)
        super().remove_command("help")
        self.db = None
        self.cur = None

    async def on_guild_join(self, guild):
        await self.db.execute("INSERT INTO guilds (guild, prefix, mention) VALUES ($1, $2, $3)", str(guild.id), ".", "1")
        await self.db.commit()
        
    async def setup_hook(self):
        await self.dbinit()
        await self.load_cogs()

    async def dbinit(self):
        print("[INFO] Connecting to database...")
        self.db = await aiosqlite.connect("database.db")
        self.cur = await self.db.cursor()
        print("[INFO] Connected to database!")
        
    async def load_cogs(self):
        print("[INFO] Loading cogs...")
        for i in os.listdir("cogs"):
            if i.endswith(".py"):
                try:
                    self.load_extension(f"cogs.{i[:-3]}")
                    print("[INFO] Loaded extension", i)
                except Exception as e:
                    print(f"[ERROR] Failed to load extension {i}: {e}")
        print("[INFO] Loaded cogs!")

    async def on_ready(self):
        print("[INFO] Running initial setup hook...")
        await self.setup_hook()
        print("[INFO] Bot is ready!")
        print(f"[STATS] Servers: {len(self.guilds)}, Commands: {len(self.commands)}, Shards: {self.shard_count}")

    async def on_command_error(self, ctx, error):
        command = self.get_command(str(ctx.message.content).replace(get_prefix(self, ctx.message), ""))
        if isinstance(error, commands.MissingRequiredArgument):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Missing argument!", description=f"Correct usage:\n```{get_prefix(self, ctx.message)}{command.usage}```")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.BotMissingPermissions):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Insufficient permissions!", description=f"I need the `{error.missing_perms.title().replace('_', ' ')}` permission to run this command!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.BadArgument):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Incorrect usage!", description=f"Correct usage:\n```{get_prefix(self, ctx.message)}{command.usage}```")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.MissingPermissions):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Missing permissions!", description=f"You need the `{error.missing_perms.title().replace('_', ' ')}` permission to run this command!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, AttributeError):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Error!", description=f"There was an error while running this command. Please report this to the developers.\n```{error}```")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.ChannelNotFound):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Channel not found!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.EmojiNotFound):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Emoji not found!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.MemberNotFound):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Member not found!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.UserNotFound):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="User not found!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, commands.RoleNotFound):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Role not found!")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, discord.Forbidden):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Insufficient permissions!", description="I can't manage that user! Please check if the bot's top role is above the highest role of the user.")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        elif isinstance(error, discord.errors.Forbidden):
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Insufficient permissions!", description="I can't manage that user! Please check if the bot's top role is above the highest role of the user.")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
        else:
            embed = discord.Embed(title="Error!", description=f"There was an error while running this command. Please report this to the developers.\n```{error}```")
            await ctx.reply(embed=embed)
            raise error

print("[INFO] Connecting to Discord...")
client = MyClient()
client.run(token)

require("Colorize")
require("Formatting")
require("Settings")
require("Components")

local pageStack = {}
local pages = {}
local menubar = nil
local footer = nil

local event, side, x, y

function waitForTouch()
    local activePage = pageStack[1]
    if activePage == nil then
        return
    end

    event, side, x, y = os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")
end

function openPage(mypage)
    table.insert(pageStack, 1, mypage)
    while true do
        local out = parallel.waitForAny(waitForTouch, displayPage)
        
        if out == 1 then
            if mypage:isInHitbox(x,y) then
                mypage:onHit(event, side, x, y)
            end
        else
            return
        end
    end
end

function displayPage()
    while pageStack[1] ~= nil do
        pageStack[1]:display()
        sleep(Settings.refreshTimer)
    end
end

--Page: title, function
--MenuPoint(page) title, function, {pages}
local PageRegion do
    Page = {
        title = "";
        components = {};
    }

    Page.__index = Page
    setmetatable(Page, ActionComp)

    function Page.new(title, components)
        local instance = setmetatable({}, Page)
        instance.title = title or ""
        instance.components = components or {}
        return instance
    end

    function Page:display()
        clear(Color.background)
        drawAlignedText(3, self.title, Alignment.center, Color.headText, Color.background)
        self:displayComponents()
    end

    function Page:displayComponents()
        for _,comp in pairs(self.components) do
            comp:display()
        end
    end

    function Page:getTitle()
        return self.title
    end

    function Page:isInHitbox(x, y)
        return true
    end

    function Page:onHit(event, side, x, y)
        for _,comp in pairs(self.components) do
            if comp:isInHitbox(x, y) then
                return comp:onHit(event, side, x ,y)
            end
        end
    end
end

local FooterBackButtonRegion do
    FooterBackButton = {}
    FooterBackButton.__index = FooterBackButton
    setmetatable(FooterBackButton, FooterBackButton)

    function FooterBackButton.new(footer)
        local instance = setmetatable({}, FooterBackButton)
        instance.parent = footer
        return instance
    end

    function FooterBackButton:display()
        local Ypos = 1
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            Ypos = MonY
        end

        drawText(1, Ypos, "[<<]", Color.footerText, self.parent.bgColor)
    end

    function FooterBackButton:isInHitbox(x, y)
        local Ypos = 1
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            Ypos = MonY
        end

        return y == Ypos and 1 <= x and  x < 5
    end

    function FooterBackButton:onHit(event, sides, x, y)
        pageBack()
    end
end

local FooterRegion do
    Footer = {}

    Footer.__index = Footer
    setmetatable(Footer, Page)

    function Footer.new(text, components)
        local instance = setmetatable({}, Footer)
        instance.text = text or ""
        instance.components = components or {}
        instance.bgColor = Color.footer
        return instance
    end

    function Footer:display()
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            drawStraightLine(1, 1, MonX, self.bgColor)
            drawAlignedText(1, self.text, Alignment.center, Color.footerText)
        else
            drawStraightLine(1, MonY, MonX, self.bgColor)
            drawAlignedText(MonY, self.text, Alignment.center, Color.footerText)
        end
        self:displayComponents()
    end

    function Footer:setColor(color)
        self.bgColor = color
    end

    function Footer:isInHitbox(x, y)
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            return y == 1
        else
            return y == MonY
        end
    end
end

local MenuButtonRegion do
    MenuButton = {}
    MenuButton.__index = MenuButton
    setmetatable(MenuButton, MenuButton)

    function MenuButton.new(title, index, bar)
        local instance = setmetatable({}, MenuButton)
        instance.title = title or "Unnamed"
        instance.index = index
        instance.parent = bar
        instance.textColor = Color.menuText
        return instance
    end

    function MenuButton:display()
        local Ypos = 1
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            Ypos = MonY
        end

        local Xpos = (self.index*(MonX/#self.parent.components) +1) or 1

        drawText(Xpos, Ypos, self.title, self.textColor, self.parent.bgColor)
    end

    function MenuButton:isInHitbox(x, y)
        local Ypos = 1
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            Ypos = MonY
        end

        local Xstart = (self.index*(MonX/#self.parent.components) +1) or 1
        local Xend = ((self.index+1)*(MonX/#self.parent.components) +1) or 1

        return y == Ypos and Xstart <= x and  x < Xend
    end
end

local MenuRegion do
    MenuBar = {}

    MenuBar.__index = MenuBar
    setmetatable(MenuBar, Page)

    function MenuBar.new(pageList)
        local instance = setmetatable({}, MenuBar)
        instance.components = pageList or {}
        instance.bgColor = Color.menubar
        return instance
    end

    function MenuBar:display()
        local pos = 1
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            pos = MonY
        end

        drawStraightLine(1, pos, MonX, self.bgColor)
        self.buttons = {}

        for i,comp in pairs(self.components) do
            local button = MenuButton.new(comp:getTitle(), i-1, self)
            function button:onHit(event, side, x, y)
                openPage(comp)
            end
            table.insert(self.buttons, button)
        end
    end

    function MenuBar:onHit(event, side, x, y)
        for i,comp in pairs(self.buttons) do
            if comp:isInHitbox(x, y) then
                comp:onHit(event, side, x, y)
            end
        end
    end

    function MenuBar:setColor(color)
        self.bgColor = color
    end

    function MenuBar:isInHitbox(x, y)
        if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
            return y == MonY
        else
            return y == 1
        end
    end

    function MenuBar:addItem(comp, pos)
        table.insert(self.components, comp, pos)
    end

    function MenuBar:removeItem(pos)
        table.remove(self.components, pos)
    end
end

local MenuPointRegion do
    MenuPoint = {}

    MenuPoint.__index = MenuPoint
    setmetatable(MenuPoint, ActionComp)

    function MenuPoint.new(title, pageList, startX)
        local instance = setmetatable({}, MenuPoint)
        instance.title = title or ""
        instance.components = {}
        instance.bgColor = Color.menuDropdown
        instance.x = startX
        for i,page in pairs(pageList) do
            local button = MenuButton.new(page.title, i, instance)
            function button:display()
                local Ypos = 1 + self.index
                if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
                    Ypos = MonY - self.index
                end

                drawText(self.x, Ypos, self.title, self.textColor, self.parent.bgColor)
            end

            function button:isInHitbox(x, y)
                local Ypos = 1 + i
                if Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation then
                    Ypos = MonY - i
                end
        
                return y == Ypos and self.x <= x and  x <= (self.x + #self.title)
            end

            function button:onHit(event, sides, x, y)
                openPage(page)
            end

            table.insert(instance.components, button)
        end
        return instance
    end

    function MenuPoint:onHit(event, side, x, y)
        for _,comp in pairs(self.components) do
            if comp:isInHitbox(x, y) then
                return comp.onHit(event, side, x ,y)
            end
        end
        pageBack()
    end
end

function miscSettings()
    while true do
        fullscreenWindow("Miscellanious Settings")

        local i = 3
        for name, value in pairs(Settings) do
            drawText(2, i, name, Color.standardText, Color.background)
            if type(value) == "number" then
                incrementor(#name + 4, i, value) --TODO
            else if type(value) == "boolean" then
                toggleButton(#name + 4, i, value)
            else if type(value) == "string" then
                textField(#name +4, i, value) --TODO
            end end end
            i = i + 1
        end

        local event, side, xPos, yPos = os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")

        if (yPos == 1 and xPos > 0 and xPos < 6 and not Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation) or (yPos == MonY and xPos > 0 and xPos < 6 and Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation) or (yPos == MonY-2 and xPos > (MonX/2)-5 and xPos < (MonX/2)+4) then
            saveSettings()
            break
        end

        --TODO interactions
    end
    pageBack()
end

function colorSettings()
    while true do
        fullscreenWindow("Color Settings")

        local versatz = 22
        local i = 3
        for name, value in pairs(Color) do
            drawText(2, i, name, Color.standardText, Color.background)
            drawText(versatz, i, "_", colors.gray, value)
            i = i + 1
        end

        local event, side, xPos, yPos = os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")

        if (yPos == 1 and xPos > 0 and xPos < 6 and not Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation) or (yPos == MonY and xPos > 0 and xPos < 6 and Settings.toggleMenuBarLocation) or (yPos == MonY-2 and xPos > (MonX/2)-5 and xPos < (MonX/2)+4) then
            saveColorConfig()
            break
        end

        if xPos == versatz then
            for name, value in pairs(Color) do
                Color[name] = selectColor(name, value)
            end
        end
    end
    pageBack()
end

function credits()
    popupWindow("Credit Page")
    local sx = MonX/6
    local sy = MonY/6

    drawAlignedText(sy+2, "Credit and Copyright", Alignment.center, Color.contrastText, Color.menuDropdown)
    
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 4, "The Code for this Script", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 5, "is Intellectual Property", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 6, "of me, SeFaGames.", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 7, "Therefore nobody is allowed", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 8, "to republish my work without", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 9, "my explicit permission.", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 10, "Despite this, you are welcome", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 11, "to modify this script for", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 12, "your personal use.", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 14, "Feel free to contact me about", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    drawText(sx+2, sy + 15, "bugs and ideas for changes.", Color.standardText, Color.menuDropdown)
    
    
    local event, side, xPos, yPos = os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")
    
    if(xPos < sx or xPos > 5*sx or yPos < sy or yPos > 5*sy or (xPos == 5*sx and yPos == sy) or (xPos >= (MonX/2)-3 and xPos <= (MonX/2)+3 and (yPos <(5*sy-1) and yPos >(5*sy)-3))) then
        pageBack()
    end
end

local function addColors()
    setColor("menu", colors.black)
    setColor("menuDropdown", colors.lightGray)
    setColor("footer", colors.black)
    setColor("footerWarning", colors.orange)
    setColor("footerError", colors.red)
    setColor("termFooter", colors.blue)
    setColor("menuText", colors.white)
    setColor("footerText", colors.gray)
end

local function addSettings()
    setSetting("toggleMenuBarPosition", false)
    setSetting("refreshTimer", 0.5)
end

addColors()
addSettings()

[PYTHON] Pastebin account scraper
content:
"""
usage: python3 script.py url
example: python3 script.py https://pastebin.com/u/nullnullnullnullnull

note that it does not scrape every page, you'll have to re-run the script for every page:
python3 script.py https://pastebin.com/u/nullnullnullnullnull/2
"""

import requests, time, sys, os
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
from queue import Queue
from threading import Thread, Event
from os.path import join, isdir, isfile
from random import uniform

if len(sys.argv) != 2:
    sys.exit(f"Usage: python3 {sys.argv[0]} url")

# feel free to add some more
lang_ext = {
    "C": "c",
    "Python": "py",
    "Ruby": "rb",
    "PHP": "php",
    "None": "txt",
    "Perl": "pl",
    "HTML": "html",
    "Bash": "sh",
    "JSON": "json",
    "AutoIt": "au3",
    "C#": "cs",
    "C++": "cpp",
    "GetText": "txt"
}

downloader_queue = Queue(256)
downloader_threads = 20
downloader_stop = Event()
downloader_ratelimited = Event()
threadbox = []

class Downloader(Thread):
    def run(self):

        while not downloader_stop.is_set():
            try:
                fname, url = downloader_queue.get(timeout=1)

                if isfile(join(profile_name, fname)):
                    continue

                if downloader_ratelimited.is_set():
                    n = uniform(2, 4)
                    print(f"[{self.name}] Ratelimited, sleeping for {n} seconds")
                    time.sleep(n)

                print(f"[{self.name}] Downloading '{fname}' from {url}")
                with requests.get(url) as req:

                    if req.status_code != 200:
                        if req.status_code == 429 or "429" in req.text:
                            downloader_ratelimited.set()

                        # re-append to queue and try later
                        downloader_queue.put((fname, url))
                        continue

                    downloader_ratelimited.clear()
                    with open(join(profile_name, fname), "w+") as fd:
                        fd.write(req.text)

                print(f"[{self.name}] Sleeping a bit as not to over-load pastebin")
                time.sleep(uniform(1, 2))

            except Exception:
                return

if __name__ == "__main__":
    profile_url = sys.argv[1]
    profile_name = profile_url.split("/u/")[-1].split("/")[0]

    with requests.get(profile_url) as req:
        if req.status_code != 200:
            sys.exit("Profile not found!")
            
        resp = req.text

    print(f"[main] Storing downloaded pastes into '{profile_name}/'")
    if not isdir(profile_name):
        os.mkdir(profile_name)
        
    print(f"[main] Starting {downloader_threads} threads")
    for _ in range(downloader_threads):
        thread = Downloader(daemon=True)
        threadbox.append(thread)
        thread.start()

    soup = BeautifulSoup(resp, "html.parser")
    main_table = soup.find("table", {"class": "maintable"})
    if not main_table:
        raise Exception("'maintable' not found")

    soup = BeautifulSoup(str(main_table), "html.parser")

    for obj in soup.findAll("tr"):
        objsoup = BeautifulSoup(str(obj), "html.parser")
        
        titleobj = objsoup.find("a", href=True)
        if not titleobj:
            continue

        title, url = titleobj.text.lstrip().rstrip().strip(), titleobj.attrs["href"]

        lang = objsoup.findAll("td", {"class": "h_800 td_smaller"})[-1]
        lang = lang.text.lstrip().rstrip().strip()

        extension = lang_ext.get(lang, "txt")

        fname = f"{title}.{extension}"
        if title.endswith(extension) or title.split(".")[-1] in lang_ext.values():
            fname = title

        downloader_queue.put(
            (fname.replace("/", "_"), f"https://pastebin.com/raw{url}")
        )

    while downloader_queue.qsize() != 0:
        print("[main] Queue is not empty yet...")
        time.sleep(1)

    print("[main] Queue emptied, setting event")
    downloader_stop.set()

    for thread in threadbox:
        thread.join()

import serial
import random
import time

def enviar_datos_puerto_serie(puerto, baud_rate, num_datos):
    try:
        # Abrir el puerto serie
        ser = serial.Serial(port=puerto, baudrate=baud_rate, timeout=1)
        print("port =",puerto,"bauds =",baud_rate)

        for _ in range(num_datos):
            # Generar dato aleatorio (puedes ajustar el rango según tus necesidades)
            dato = random.randint(0, 100)

            # Convertir el dato a bytes antes de enviarlo
            dato_bytes = bytes([dato])

            # Enviar el dato por el puerto serie
           # ser.write(dato_bytes)
            ser.write(dato_bytes)
            print("data send:",dato)

            # Esperar un tiempo para evitar sobrecargar el puerto
            time.sleep(0.5)

        # Cerrar el puerto serie cuando hayamos terminado
        ser.close()
        print("Close com.")

    except serial.SerialException as e:
        print("Erreur opening port ",puerto, "erreur ",e)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    puerto_serie = '/dev/ttyUSB3'  # Reemplaza 'COM1' con el nombre de tu puerto serie (ejemplo para Windows)
    tasa_baudios = 9600    # Ajusta la tasa de baudios según la configuración de tu dispositivo
    num_datos_enviar = 10  # Número de datos aleatorios que deseas enviar

    enviar_datos_puerto_serie(puerto_serie, tasa_baudios, num_datos_enviar)
